Drag the symbol on the top-right to the left, there should be a rebuild button on that panel

>>ee1582fb-a1ec-4845-931b-a6bbcd0b9ba3
Maybe OP needs to know this:
Zeronet is a peer-to-peer network, so you need to leave the service on for a while until some people have downloaded the files fully. Otherwise people will just see your post with missing files.
